extendedInfo.description: Do you think you have a discerning eye? Are you a gumshoe at heart? Put it to the test with this unique hidden object game. Be the first to play the first ever hidden number game on Android.Find the numbers hidden inside the eye catching images.The Lost Numbers Features:*Compatible on all Android devices with screen resolution      size 240X320, 320X480, 480X800, 480X854, 1024X600, 1280X720,  1280X800 pixels.* Unique Hidden Object Game to play* Explore unique scene to explore* Unique game at every try.* Resume the game from the last scene.* Handy hint option available.* Highly addictive game play.* Replay scene and beat the best time* Compatible on Google Nexus 7 phone and tablet,Galaxy S2,Galaxy S3 and other similar devicesHow to play:This game constitutes catchy images with numbers hidden in between them. The user has to find out only the required numbers from the list below. You can zoom In and Out. To unlock the consecutive chapters, the user has to clear the level . You can also make use of the available Hint option to find out the required numbers but remember that you can use hint only  once in a minute. Showcasing stimulating themes and fantastic graphics, you will easily get caught up in this detailed and real catchy seek and find game.The app is projected to do well as it does apply to casual gamers across different ages. It should also appeal to young children as the graphics and the objects have been designed keeping them in mind.Try it out and we bet that you wonât get bored as every time you will have to find new numbers on the screen within a given limit of time.This application is brought to you totally free with the help of search monetization. I have opted to use this to be able to keep creating more free apps for you. Please note that with this app you will receive a few search points on your device, all are easily deleted or replaced. Thank you for your understanding.This free app is ad supported and may contain ads in the notification tray and/or home screen.
